OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening, one or two thundery
OL,7,Fshower possible across the northwest.
OL,8,FShowers or longer spells of rain
OL,9,Fbecoming more widespread overnight in
OL,10,Fwest, but drier in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FThe west will see showers or
OL,13,Flonger spells of rain, occasionally
OL,14,Fheavy. Drier in the east with some
OL,15,Fbrightness along the Moray Firth
OL,16,Fcoast. Brisk west or southwesterly
OL,17,Fwinds. Cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
